                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d621">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Whitehouse</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Blaine</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rome</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-03-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 15, 1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Whitehouse informs Mr. Blaine that the news from New Orleans had deeply moved
                    the Italian Government, which urges the President to use every exertion possible
                    to protect Italians.</p>
            </div>
